{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Access-Control-Allow-Origin","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Access-Control-Allow-Origin","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"><code><strong>Access-Control-Allow-Origin</strong></code>&nbsp;响应头指定了该响应的资源是否被允许与给定的<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Origin\">origin</a>共享。</div>\n\n<div id=\"sect2\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<table class=\"properties\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Header type</th>\n   <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Response_header\">Response header</a></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Forbidden_header_name\">Forbidden header name</a></th>\n   <td>no</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"语法","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">Access-Control-Allow-Origin: *\nAccess-Control-Allow-Origin: &lt;origin&gt;\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"指令","title":"指令","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"sect3\">*</dt>\n <dd>对于不需具备凭证（credentials）的请求，服务器会以“<code>*</code>”作为通配符，从而允许所有域都具有访问资源的权限。</dd>\n <dt id=\"origin\">&lt;origin&gt;</dt>\n <dd>指定一个可以访问资源的 URI。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":"<p>如需允许所有资源都可以访问<code>您</code>的资源，您可以如此设置：</p>\n\n<pre class=\"notranslate\">Access-Control-Allow-Origin: *</pre>\n\n<p>如需允许<code>https://developer.mozilla.org</code>访问您的资源，您可以设置：</p>\n\n<pre class=\"notranslate\">Access-Control-Allow-Origin: https://developer.mozilla.org</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"cors和缓存","title":"CORS 和缓存","isH3":true,"content":"<p>如果服务器未使用“<code>*</code>”，而是指定了一个域，那么为了向客户端表明服务器的返回会根据<code>Origin</code>请求头而有所不同，必须在<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Vary\"><code>Vary</code></a>响应头中包含<code>Origin</code>。</p>\n\n<pre class=\"notranslate\">Access-Control-Allow-Origin: https://developer.mozilla.org\nVary: Origin</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"规范","title":"规范","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">规范</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">状态</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">注释</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://fetch.spec.whatwg.org/#http-access-control-allow-origin\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Fetch<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">Access-Control-Allow-Origin</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Living Standard</span></td>\n   <td>初始定义</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"data":null,"query":"http/headers/access-control-allow-origin","browsers":null}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参见","title":"参见","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Origin\"><code>Origin</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Vary\"><code>Vary</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"语法","id":"语法"},{"text":"指令","id":"指令"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"参见","id":"参见"}],"summary":"如需允许所有资源都可以访问您的资源，您可以如此设置：","popularity":0.0013,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Access-Control-Allow-Origin","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Access-Control-Allow-Origin","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Access-Control-Allow-Origin","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Access-Control-Allow-Origin","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Access-Control-Allow-Origin","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Access-Control-Allow-Origin","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Access-Control-Allow-Origin","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/http/headers/access-control-allow-origin","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/http/headers/access-control-allow-origin/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP","title":"HTTP"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers","title":"HTTP Headers"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Access-Control-Allow-Origin","title":"Access-Control-Allow-Origin"}],"pageTitle":"Access-Control-Allow-Origin - HTTP | MDN","noIndexing":false}}